<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #00A5E3;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .message {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .reset-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #00A5E3;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .reset-button:hover {
            background-color: #0088b3;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="message">
                <p>Hello <strong><%= fullName %></strong>,</p>
                
                <p>We received a request to reset your password for your account associated with <strong><%= email %></strong>.</p>
                
                <p>Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
                
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="<%= reset_link %>" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
                </div>
                
                <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
                <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #00A5E3;"><%= reset_link %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <strong>Important:</strong> This link will expire in 30 minutes for security reasons. If you don't reset your password within this time, you'll need to request a new reset link.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
                
                <p>For security reasons, this link can only be used once. After you reset your password, this link will no longer be valid.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 QuickCourt. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
